<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>开户籍的工具</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .description {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        
        .input-group {
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border 0.3s;
        }
        
        input:focus {
            border-color: #3498db;
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.2);
        }
        
        button {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #2c3e50);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        button:disabled {
            background: #95a5a6;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
        }
        
        .loading {
            display: none;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .spinner {
            border: 5px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 5px solid #3498db;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }
        
        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        .result {
            display: none;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>开户籍的工具</h1>
        
        <div class="description">
            <p>请输入东山中学学生的姓名进行查询。系统将验证该学生的户籍信息。</p>
            <p>注意：本系统仅支持查询东山中学在校学生的户籍信息。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="input-group">
            <label for="studentName">学生姓名：</label>
            <input type="text" id="studentName" placeholder="请输入学生姓名">
        </div>
        
        <button id="queryBtn">查询户籍信息</button>
        
        <div class="loading" id="loading">
            <div class="spinner"></div>
            <p>正在查询中，请稍候...</p>
            <p>系统正在验证学生信息并查询户籍数据</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="result" id="result">
            <h3>系统公告</h3>
            <p>网页正在维护中，请于次日18:00后使用。</p>
            <p>给您带来的不便，敬请谅解。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            注意：本工具仅供授权人员使用，未经授权访问将追究法律责任。
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2023 户籍查询系统 | 仅限内部使用</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('queryBtn').addEventListener('click', function() {
            const studentName = document.getElementById('studentName').value.trim();
            
            if (!studentName) {
                alert('请输入学生姓名！');
                return;
            }
            
            // 禁用按钮
            this.disabled = true;
            this.textContent = '查询中...';
            
            // 显示加载动画
            document.getElementById('loading').style.display = 'block';
            
            // 设置3分钟（180000毫秒）后显示结果
            setTimeout(function() {
                // 隐藏加载动画
                document.getElementById('loading').style.display = 'none';
                
                // 显示结果
                document.getElementById('result').style.display = 'block';
                
                // 恢复按钮状态
                document.getElementById('queryBtn').disabled = false;
                document.getElementById('queryBtn').textContent = '查询户籍信息';
            }, 180000); // 3分钟 = 180000毫秒
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
